{"tid":1507934,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"暗乜撚野黑文宣啫 想輸咪出聲囉","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:22.000Z","uid":308041,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0782ea3f39750aa22e6979458e3784da512a0082","tid":1507934,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"我同你班想放fake new嘅人講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚制呀</span></span><br />\n外國外媒支持我地係因為我地有良知<br />\n入立法會俾錢買野飲 唔破壞文物<br />\n遊行完自發執垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係暴徒 我地係有底線<br />\n我地不能夠活成我地最憎嘅人呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人會話我地有民意<br />\n光環又攞晒<br />\n唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家係但外國唔係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地依家每個一舉一動都喺世界嘅注視之下<br />\n我地一旦變得同黑警一樣<br />\n咁我地就已經唔會有人記得我地做過嘅好事<br />\n記得我地係為自由民主而戰<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚再話乜鳩暗黑文宣<br />\n因為講真話先係我地最大嘅武器</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4681bc0284f593dfbfbd0979a0110c650e00f","tid":1507934,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=8ea72cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=